約完就算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:16:44.000Z","msg":"商業角度嚟講係，老闆都有咁既打算同覺悟。但而家係一間有表態既黃店結業，我都見證住老闆有出心出力過做文宣幫助手足。我覺得係呢點都無咩好質疑，我只希望係手足既，就盡量幫襯一下，等老闆唔好蝕咁多，帶返幾個錢結業，當然手足都有自由選擇唔去幫襯，所以我都希望其他人都行去兜個圈，拎本佢地有提供既《牆紙》走都好，我相信老闆都會開心既"},{"pid":"b3c1afb0911630a47ff5ec7e423265c76c73ef41","tid":1919183,"uid":187852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:17:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54aaf02184df11d4ef71ae007e0c7beefd71e45","tid":1919183,"uid":149877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:17:23.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"8546f203f5c424cb37359c6fff026e630f5f3b7d","tid":1919183,"uid":187852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:20:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c0efaa32027616080161a0201c5124b21834811","tid":1919183,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:21:03.000Z","msg":"租貴都無計, 大家幫到就幫."},{"pid":"d0f5d6b7472b33506f0a1c491f7f97f000f5abe0","tid":1919183,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:21:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"656f905f5240552dbb2292ccbe606091c7b769a2","tid":1919183,"uid":18177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:21:40.000Z","msg":"唔係唔想幫，D貨咁樣真係好難買得落手<br />\n<br />\n加上旁邊都係d呃人mk電話舖，印象麻麻"},{"pid":"829888a71c91f1b540d3942b3e5fae98161c2809","tid":1919183,"uid":80950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"656f905f5240552dbb2292ccbe606091c7b769a2","tid":1919183,"uid":18177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:21:40.000Z","msg":"唔係唔想幫，D貨咁樣真係好難買得落手<br />\n<br />\n加上旁邊都係d呃人mk電話舖，印象麻麻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:25:40.000Z","msg":"幫得就幫啦 大家都係盡做 買唔落手咪都share下 總有野支持到既<img 